sentences.en: Even further south, reflections from 35 km depth may correspond to the Moho of peninsular India.
sentences.cn: 再往南从35公里深度来的反射波是来自印度半岛的莫霍界面。

sentences.en: Tensions on the Korean peninsular and Burma's planned elections are to dominate a meeting of South East Asian foreign ministers in Hanoi, Vietnam.
sentences.cn: 在越南首都河内举行的东南亚外交部长会议上将讨论朝鲜半岛的紧张局势和缅甸有计划的选举。

sentences.en: The Strait of Johor separates Singapore from Peninsular Malaysia.
sentences.cn: 新加坡和马来西亚半岛之间隔着柔佛海峡.

sentences.en: They never signed a peace treaty after the conflict on the Korean Peninsular in the 1950 s.
sentences.cn: 自1950年在朝鲜半岛冲突之后,他们从未签定和平条约.

trans.tran_cn: 半岛（状）的（居民），形成半岛的
